name: Ash Ra Tempel
description: '''Ash Ra Tempel''' was a German [[krautrock]] group led by guitarist [[Manuel Göttsching]] that was active from 1970 to 1976. Their debut album ''[[Ash Ra Tempel (album)|Ash Ra Tempel]]'' was released in 1971. Following the band's demise, Göttsching released music under the name [[Ashra (band)|Ashra]].
